    "accordions_LrLbTK": {
      "type": "accordions",
      "blocks": {
        "content_KjJnfW": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What makes Jolene Coffee different from other cold brews?",
            "content": "<p>We slow-brew our Fair Trade certified beans for twenty-four hours using only two premium ingredients. This process creates a smooth, balanced flavor without the harsh acidity found in rushed brewing methods. No artificial flavors, no unnecessary additives.</p>",
            "icon": "",
            "color_scheme": "btn",
            "enable_open": true
          }
        },
        "content_Kqy98Q": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How should I serve Jolene Coffee?",
            "content": "<p>Our Black Cold Brew is perfect over ice or at room temperature. The Oat Milk Latte is ready to drink straight from the bottle. Both can be enjoyed hot if you prefer - just warm gently without boiling to preserve the flavor.</p>",
            "icon": "",
            "color_scheme": "btn",
            "enable_open": false
          }
        },
        "content_3jkmy8": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is Jolene Coffee organic and non-GMO?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, all our ingredients are verified non-GMO and our coffee beans are Fair Trade certified. We source directly from farmers who share our commitment to sustainable, ethical growing practices.</p>",
            "icon": "",
            "color_scheme": "btn",
            "enable_open": false
          }
        },
        "content_ngLB3x": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long does Jolene Coffee stay fresh?",
            "content": "<p>Unopened bottles stay fresh for up to 6 months when stored in a cool, dry place. Once opened, refrigerate and consume within 7 days for optimal flavor. The date on each bottle shows the peak freshness window.</p>",
            "icon": "",
            "color_scheme": "btn",
            "enable_open": false
          }
        },
        "content_9WdCEU": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you offer subscriptions?",
            "content": "<p>Absolutely. Subscribe and save 15% on every order with free shipping. You can modify, skip, or cancel your subscription anytime through your account. Most subscribers choose monthly delivery to never run out of great coffee.</p>",
            "icon": "",
            "color_scheme": "btn",
            "enable_open": false
          }
        },
        "content_GDRarW": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Where do you ship and how much does it cost?",
            "content": "<p>We ship nationwide with free shipping on orders over $35. Subscription orders always ship free. Orders typically arrive within 3-5 business days, and we'll send tracking information once your order ships.</p>",
            "icon": "",
            "color_scheme": "btn",
            "enable_open": false
          }
        }
      },
