          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>I've been drinking cold brew for years but nothing compares to Jolene. The Black is my morning ritual now - smooth, bold, never bitter. Finally found my perfect coffee.</p>",
            "title": "<p>Marcus T., Strategy Director</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_4m7Eq8": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The Oat Milk Latte tastes like it came from my favorite coffee shop. I keep a case in my fridge and it's become my afternoon pick-me-up. Creamy perfection.</p>",
            "title": "<p>Sarah K., Yoga Instructor</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_wUztfP": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Mix Pack is genius. Black when I need that bold hit, White when I want something smooth and creamy. Both are incredible. This coffee has ruined me for everything else.</p>",
            "title": "<p>David R., Entrepreneur</p>"
          }
        }
